get.summary:
One-shot HTTP fetch of the same payload streamed by the WS endpoint.
Use this for initial page loads or environments that can't open a WS;
the WS at `/owner/{owner}/ws` is the live source of truth.

post.summary:
Atomically close the current position and open the opposite side, in one tx.
Proceeds from the close settle into the opposite-side's collateral custody;
a 2% haircut absorbs price drift between quote and execution.
